<div class="main-visual">
      <div class="content">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="offset6 span4 intro">
              <h4 class="offseted-content">Why Game books?</h4>
              <p class="offseted-content">
                We decided to do this about gamebooks because they are a different kind of entertainment, away from the mindless shooter
                or the repetitive grinder games as of late.
              </p>
              <h5 class="offseted-content">A few more points</h5>
              <p class="offseted-content">
                <ul>
                  <li>Game books invoke a tought process like a real book.</li>
                  <li>They are not always that burdening as a novel , and give you a sence of control</li>
                  <li>We try to break the dogma of games by taking them away from the current <i>Call of Shooter</i></li>
                </ul>
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <video autoplay="autoplay" src="/video/mainvisual1.mp4" id="video" loop="loop">
      </video>
</div>

<div class="bg2">
